---
// 3. Compare - "the usual" vs Lingo7 Realty (rows reveal on scroll).
---
<section class="compare" id="why">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section__title" data-i18n="compare.title"><strong class="hero__hl">Study in your own language.</strong> Take the exam in&nbsp;English.</h2>
    <p class="section__subtitle" data-i18n="compare.subtitle"><strong class="hero__hl">You understand the material right away.</strong> Then the app helps you practice the questions until they feel&nbsp;easy.</p>
    <div class="compare__list">

      <div class="compare__row">
        <div class="compare__old">
          <span class="compare__label compare__label--old" data-i18n="compare.row1.old-label">❌ The usual</span>
          <strong data-i18n="compare.row1.old-title">Everything is in English only</strong>
          <p data-i18n="compare.row1.old-text">The book, the words, the questions, the answers. All in English. You spend your energy on the language, not on the material.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="compare__arrow">→</div>
        <div class="compare__new">
          <span class="compare__label compare__label--new" data-i18n="compare.row1.new-label">✅ Lingo7 Realty</span>
          <strong data-i18n="compare.row1.new-title">Translation built in</strong>
          <p data-i18n="compare.row1.new-text">Everything comes with a translation in your language. You understand it at once.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="compare__row">
        <div class="compare__old">
          <span class="compare__label compare__label--old" data-i18n="compare.row2.old-label">❌ The usual</span>
          <strong data-i18n="compare.row2.old-title">Hundreds of terms and questions. Too many to remember</strong>
          <p data-i18n="compare.row2.old-text">When you just cram, you learn one thing and forget another.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="compare__arrow">→</div>
        <div class="compare__new">
          <span class="compare__label compare__label--new" data-i18n="compare.row2.new-label">✅ Lingo7 Realty</span>
          <strong data-i18n="compare.row2.new-title">Cards that help you remember</strong>
          <p data-i18n="compare.row2.new-text">The app shows each term again just before you forget it. This is a proven way to remember.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="compare__row">
        <div class="compare__old">
          <span class="compare__label compare__label--old" data-i18n="compare.row3.old-label">❌ The usual</span>
          <strong data-i18n="compare.row3.old-title">Every new word slows you down</strong>
          <p data-i18n="compare.row3.old-text">You stop, you lose focus, and you learn more slowly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="compare__arrow">→</div>
        <div class="compare__new">
          <span class="compare__label compare__label--new" data-i18n="compare.row3.new-label">✅ Lingo7 Realty</span>
          <strong data-i18n="compare.row3.new-title">One simple flow: question → translation → review</strong>
          <p data-i18n="compare.row3.new-text">It all happens in one place. The language stops getting in the way. You stay focused and learn faster.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
